value.name: Off the Grid: Million Dollar Manhunt
value.original_name: Off the Grid: Million Dollar Manhunt
value.overview: Off the Grid: Million Dollar Manhunt is a game show which airs on The History Channel. Contestants attempt to evade Kevin Reeve, an expert in surveillance, fugitive tracking, and classified government technologies. If they can succeed in performing simple tasks, for one day, and avoid detection, they win $1 million.
